reviewText: Great if you don't like science based on evidence and reality.
Love these videos.  Great for the kids!
Oh My Goodness!  You have got to order these Creation Proclaims series DVDs!  They are great!

Love this series ( volume 1-3) and I heard they have volume 4 out.  The BEST EVER series on creation science with TOP QUALITY video and easy to understand explanations geared for the younger audience but enjoyed by all ages!!  We LOVE these DVD's and have watched them several times.
